{{Infobox Website | name = The Kurdish Digital Library | logo = [[Image:Logobnk.png|200px|Kurdish Institute of Paris]] | url = [http://bnk.institutkurde.org/?l=en bnk.institutkurde.org] | commercial = No | type = Digital library | language = multilingual | owner = [[Kurdish Institute of Paris]] | launch date = December 10, 2010 | current status = Active }}
'''The Kurdish Digital Library''' ''(called BNK, in French La bibliothèque numérique kurde (BNK))'' is a multimedia digital library created by [[Kurdish Institute of Paris]]. The Digital Library consists of writings about the [[Kurds]] and [[Kurdistan]]. Its aim is to make the Kurdish cultural heritage available as digital data.<ref>Kurdistan Commentary https://kurdistancommentary.wordpress.com/2010/12/10/kurdish-digital-library-now-online/</ref>
